{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4d57547bca","title":"对《人民日报》社论稿《克服右倾情绪，厉行增产节约》的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"25e7af63cd","index":0,"year":1959,"month":8,"day":5,"articleId":"4d57547bca"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"fade07a37d","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4d57547bca","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是新华通讯社社长、《人民日报》总编辑吴冷西遵照毛泽东指示起草的一篇《人民日报》社论稿。原题为《克服松劲情绪，厉行增产节约》，毛泽东审阅时改为《克服右倾情绪，厉行增产节约》。"},{"id":"6fbd12c613","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4d57547bca","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇二中用宋体字排印的是毛泽东改写的文字。此外，毛泽东对社论稿还作了个别文字上的修改。"},{"id":"94ddcdb36a","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4d57547bca","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这篇社论于1959年8月6日在《人民日报》发表。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d8a223a0cf","type":"title","text":"对《人民日报》社论稿（克服右倾情绪，厉行增产节约》的批语和修改吗","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4d57547bca"},{"id":"fade07a37d","type":"paragraph","text":"即送吴冷西同志。如六日来不及见报，七日见报也可","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4d57547bca"},{"id":"6fbd12c613","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4d57547bca"},{"id":"94ddcdb36a","type":"paragraph","text":"八月五日下午十一时半","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4d57547bca"},{"id":"4b6511292f","type":"paragraph","text":"抓紧八、九两个月，进一步展开一个轰轰烈烈的增产节约运动，鼓足干劲，坚决反对在一部分干部中新近抬头的石倾情绪，努力完成和超额完成今年的跃进计划——这是工业、农业、运输业、商业等经济战线上当前的迫切任务。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4d57547bca"}],"page":{"id":"e3c861804b","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"4d57547bca","start":257,"end":258}}}},"__N_SSG":true}